      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "The 2YOs kick us off. SUPER WONDER (2) is a Supido colt out of a handy dam, who has produced her share of winners. Hails from the sharp juvenile stable of R & C Jolly and is expected to hit the ground running off the back of two sharp hitouts. Stablemate CRAZYABOUTZOU (5) is a Zousain filly on debut. Closed nicely behind Never Ordinary in a lead-up trial and the form has since been franked with a brilliant debut by the trial winner in the Cinderella Stakes last week, beaten a lip. Gets in light with the claim and can make a bright start. CHICA ASTUTA (4) is a Toronado filly from the Stokes camp on debut. Has come along nicely at the jumpouts and can make a bright start. CYCLOTRON (1) is a Hellbent gelding for the McEvoy team on debut. Has jumped out well in readiness, without being asked a great deal. No shock to see him right there. HARMONIK (6) is a Capitalist filly debuting. Finished just behind CRAZYABOUTZOU in trial and has since won a jumpout. This looks tough but keeping safe.",
